data.description: Gnome Stock Icons in XPM format
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
Very often, people ask where to get the Gnome stock icons. To make
    it convenient for Gtk-Perl developers, this is a module with all
    stock icons in array format, converted from the Gnome library
    source.

    Gnome::StockIcons seems like the logical self-documenting name.

    Wim
